node.text:
In this episode we present new models for XDiavel and Scrambler.
Two very different worlds, but having one thing in common: a very strong personality.
On the one hand, the world of the XDiavel, the cruiser as defined by Ducati: elegant, refined, low seat, forward footpegs, high torque engine, so that sportiness typical of Ducati, is always ready.
On the other hand, the Land of Joy of Scrambler: easy, fun, an extraordinary mix of tradition and modernity, the carefree way to truly enjoy your bike.
